data.description: Fantastic property with a sparkling pool & no neighbors behind you! The green space was a former golf course, offering lovely views and privacy. You will feel welcomed in by the large foyer, expansive living room with luxury vinyl plank flooring, abundant natural light, a wood burning fireplace and wet bar. Bright and airy sunroom with extra under stair storage. Spacious dining space has sight lines to the living room giving a great feel for entertaining. Eat-in kitchen with island, double oven, granite countertops, breakfast area & sitting space. Oversized master bedroom with sitting area, abundant storage, updated shower, jetted tub & two walk-in closets. Spacious secondary bedrooms with step-in closets. Laundry room off of garage with built cabinets down. Upstairs game room with full bath, wet bar & large closet! Enjoy the covered back porch with wrought iron fence, gated separately from pool area. New roof, new duct work, and Window World fold-in windows!
